      "id": 8,
      "options": {
        "code": {
          "language": "markdown",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "### Runtime alert threshold reference\n\n- **ObservMeHighLlmErrorRate:** LLM error ratio > **5%** for 10m.\n- **ObservMeHighToolFailureRate:** per-tool failure ratio > **10%** for 10m.\n- **ObservMeSubagentSpawnFailures:** any subagent spawn failures for 10m.\n- **ObservMeExportDropsDetected:** `sum(rate(observme_telemetry_dropped_total[5m])) > 0` for 5m.\n- **ObservMeCostSpike:** LLM spend increase > **$50** in 1h for 15m; tune per budget.\n- **ObservMeRedactionFailures:** `sum(rate(observme_redaction_failures_total[5m])) > 0` for 5m.\n- **ObservMeRunawayAgentFanOut:** p95 fan-out > **20** over 10m.\n- **ObservMeExcessiveAgentTreeDepth:** p95 tree depth > **5** over 10m.\n- **ObservMeOrphanAgentsDetected:** orphan-agent rate over 10m is warning.\n- **ObservMeTraceContextPropagationFailures:** propagation failures over 10m are warning.\n- **ObservMeActiveAgentsStuckHigh:** active agents > **100** for 30m; tune per deployment.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.1.0",
      "title": "Alert threshold reference",
      "type": "text"
